Open "Javascript" on my GitHub page.
Select "Raw"
CTRL + A, CTRL + C
Double tap (or right-click) an empty space in your bookmarks bar. 
(If it is full of bookmarks, then go to the right-end of the bookmarks bar between the last bookmark and the drop-down arrow for the rest of your bookmarks)
Select "Add page..."
Name > Optional : URL > Press CTRL + V
Select "Save"
CTRL + T, search "about:blank"
Select the bookmark you made containing the Javascript on the "about:blank" page
Have fun :)
